        "img_text": "Hammered Patterns for Unique Durability",
        "info_header1": "Hardness That Lasts",
        "info_content1": "~60 ±1 HRC",
        "info_footer1": "Engineered for professional use, this hardness provides superior edge retention. It balances strength, resilience, and lasting sharpness in heavy kitchen work.",
