          "settings": {
            "title": "Safety",
            "image1": "shopify://shop_images/Icons_7_83874bec-26fe-425f-b920-8445d6bbc6f1.png",
            "content1": "<p>The burnt white oak + red G10 handle <strong>provides secure, ergonomic grip</strong>—reduces slipping, improves control, especially when wet, reducing risk of accidents.</p>",
            "image2": "shopify://shop_images/Icons_8_080f7da8-6612-4a45-af5b-dbcc396e4685.png",
            "content2": "<p>Outer layers using 316L stainless steel <strong>ensure the blade meets food-contact safety norms</strong> (resisting corrosion, no harmful leaching ), maintaining hygiene and safety with each use.</p>",
            "image3": "shopify://shop_images/Icons_9_d9044487-9e9d-4768-8784-2bb2c15e3e8c.png",
            "content3": "<p>The heat-treated, cryo-tempered blade <strong>maintains hardness without brittleness</strong>—edge retention means less sharpening and safer maintenance.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
