            "accordion_row_seo0": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "t:names.accordion_dash_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "What makes the Mo Series special?",
                "content": "<p>The Mo Series combines a VG10 steel core with 67 layers of Damascus cladding. VG10 is one of the most popular kitchen knife steels in the world, developed by Japan's Takefu Special Steel. The 67-layer Damascus isn't just visual, it adds corrosion resistance and helps food release from the blade surface.</p>",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
