                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "t:names.text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>The Mo Series combines a VG10 steel core with 67 layers of Damascus cladding. VG10 is one of the most popular kitchen knife steels in the world, developed by Japan's Takefu Special Steel. The 67-layer Damascus isn't just visual, it adds corrosion resistance and helps food release from the blade surface.</p>",
