            "accordion_row_seo2": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "t:names.accordion_dash_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "How do I care for the Damascus pattern?",
                "content": "<p>The Damascus pattern is permanent and won't wash off with normal use. To keep it looking its best: hand wash immediately after use, dry thoroughly, and avoid prolonged contact with acidic foods (lemon, tomato) which can cause temporary discolouration. Over time, a natural patina may develop that actually enhances the pattern contrast. See our <a href=\"/blogs/news/how-to-care-for-damascus-steel-knives\">Damascus care guide</a>.</p>",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
