              "settings": {
                "heading": "Is the Mo Series a good gift?",
                "content": "<p>The Mo Series is our most popular gift choice. The striking Damascus pattern makes an immediate visual impression, while the VG10 performance ensures the recipient will use it daily. Each knife comes in a premium gift box. See our <a href=\"/blogs/news/kitchen-knife-gift-guide\">kitchen knife gift guide</a> for pairing suggestions.</p>",
